{"tid":1540580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[膊頭有花入]大家應該調轉分析下，林鄭撤回有咩壞處，針住春袋黎打，破壞佢既算盤","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:50:46.000Z","uid":261300,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5a425b1396ff2fce95bcda6223d539a6d99c02","tid":1540580,"uid":261300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"每一個決定都會有好有壞，如果撤回對林鄭咁有利，點解遲遲都唔肯撤回?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[六大陰謀］林鄭宣布撤回反送中的陰謀<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n睇完呢個我覺得好多都合理，但如果講左撤回會變咁有利既狀況點解林鄭要咁遲先講呢兩隻字?如果係7月頭講我諗好多人都會收貨。可惜佢錯過左時機，咁我認為一定會有D因素令佢唔肯講呢兩隻字。<br />\n第一:<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸怕應承左我地，大陸人會有樣學樣</span></span>;支那人一早有吹風話中國比得太多特權香港，對香港人太好，仲有好多支那人叫出解放軍比亂。既然政府E家講左撤回，相信<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多支那人都唔倨</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地更應該向佢地輸出革命，學香港爭取下就有，同時令佢地對香港既不滿增加。<br />\n<br />\n第二:<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有藍絲支持政府強硬對付示威</span></strong></span>;好多藍絲都死硬派，覺得自已同政府岩哂，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢個更加係我地分化既好時機，政府咁軟弱，叫藍絲情何以堪</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地應該加強文宣恥笑一下藍絲，等佢地都對政府反感。<br />\n<br />\n第三:<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭多次講過唔會撤回，如果撤回左就係出而反而，令更加多人唔信佢</span></strong></span>;如果林鄭講過既野唔算數，對狗隊市氣將會係一大打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，林鄭話唔會設立獨立調查委員會，狗狗你信唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地要加強文宣，削弱警隊市氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，大家要提防商家佬，撤回左商家佬同我地既目標已經未必一致，我地要堅持抵制藍絲店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，多D幫襯愛香港既店令商家堅持同我地同一陣線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油，佢退讓就證明左我地既抗爭係有價值，要堅持落力，光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"290f1e6a798de73bf4667d83f99203834d3aa19b","tid":1540580,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"簡單D黎講<br />\n就係分化所有敵對勢力既好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5becbb08db8c97f915244ea22cb417fad98173d2","tid":1540580,"uid":261300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"290f1e6a798de73bf4667d83f99203834d3aa19b","tid":1540580,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"簡單D黎講<br />\n就係分化所有敵對勢力既好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"10/10<br />\n簡而精"},{"pid":"17a28e1c127dccb7d1e57f67e67f110196719985","tid":1540580,"uid":311991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推推推"},{"pid":"155c4f127b00a78c56c69e68e0f0f82053a8c75b","tid":1540580,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffa406b3c0ee440f775537c8f2f632699eba3875","tid":1540580,"uid":261300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"求推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />p牌推唔起"},{"pid":"7b0be3c1a0322394c6e8c7eb0771989c90ff956a","tid":1540580,"uid":261300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"文宣全面進場"},{"pid":"68da5df8ca829ac1e91f63e53ad275f7d72c289e","tid":1540580,"uid":169116,"li